        <% end %>
        <p class="indent-address"><%= @company.city %>, <%= @company.state %> <%= @company.zip %></p>
        <p><b>Consignee email:</b></p>
        <p class="indent-address">cpsoinos@mac.com</p>
        <p>Unofficial correspondence may be made by phone or text to:</p>
        <p class="indent-address">(978) 835-8015   (Carole Psoinos)</p>
        <p><b>Consignor phone:</b></p>
        <p class="indent-address"><%= @client.phone %></p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Entire Agreement:</b>  This Agreement represents the entire consignment agreement between the Parties, and shall supersede all prior agreements, understandings, and representations by either Party regarding consignment. 
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>No Implied Waiver:</b>  The waiver of any breach of any obligation, term or condition of this Agreement shall not be deemed to constitute a waiver of any preceding or succeeding breach of the same or any other obligation, term or condition of this Agreement. 
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Severability:</b>  The invalidity or unenforceability of any provision of this Agreement shall not affect the validity or enforceability of any other provision of this Agreement. 
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Counterparts and Electronic Signatures:</b>  If this Agreement is executed in separate parts, the separate parts shall together constitute an enforceable contract. Electronic or digital signatures shall constitute valid enforceable signatures. 
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Headings:</b>  The headings contained in this Agreement are for convenience purposes only and shall not affect, in any way, the meaning or interpretation of this Agreement. 
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Governing Law:</b>  This Agreement shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Massachusetts.
      </li>
    </ol>

